name: Terraforming
body:
## Model transforming tools for Java 8
A library of tools making common model transforming tasks easy and safe.

Includes:
* Domain-DTO bidierctioanl transforming
* Safe enum transforming helpers

### Documentation
See wiki articles <https://github.com/InterstellarOcean/terraforming/wiki>

### Releases
Latest release 0.1 <http://search.maven.org/#artifactdetails%7Corg.interstellarocean%7Cterraforming%7C0.1%7Cjar>

Other releases <http://search.maven.org/#search%7Cga%7C1%7Cg%3A%22org.interstellarocean%22%20a%3A%22terraforming%22>
